The paper focuses on the security challenges of cyber-physical systems, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). It also discusses the components and systems of CPS, which can be classified under systems and control (cs.SY) and software engineering (cs.SE). The paper also mentions the use of AI in CPS security, which can be categorized under artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper discusses the potential sources of attacks and ways of protection, which can be classified under networking and internet architecture (cs.NI).
